data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION SELLER IS MOTIVATED!!!THE MOST UNIQUE AND STUNNING PROPERTY ON THE MARKET CAN BE YOURS!  Elegantly reimagined home with "hacienda feel" , resort style seclusion and privacy, nestled in Whittier on 13647 Jackson St.  Inside, the charm is evident with "high end" 3/4 Dutch front door, glorious chandelier lighting, custom handcrafted wood ceilings, formal dining area & French doors ,all which open directly to the embracing side deck and extended walk way.  Classic style custom built sidebar accentuates the hallway that sways to the brand new kitchen and highly desirable CAFE brand appliances.  Ambient lighting filters throughout this home. The primary bedroom suite exudes luxury with huge walk in closet, classic soaking tub, walk in shower with rainfall effect, and private courtyard  Enjoy morning coffee and solitude in the sunlit cozy kitchen nook.  The main house has 3 bedrooms and 2 baths and above the garage is bonus room that adds an additional 387 sq ft. currently used as a bedroom. (owner had planned to add bathroom and kitchenette to this unit for ADU. Buyers to perform their own due diligence on this matter) Total square footage taped by appraisal in 2022 is 1919 sq.ft this includes the 1532 of main house and 387 sq. ft. of the bonus room over the garage. Buyer's to confirm all data independently.  This is a must see property.    (note* first bathroom has been completely remodeled and waiting for few items delivery to finish) PLEASE SEE VIRTUAL TOUR.
